These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, indonesian
1. the indonesian is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the indonesian is between the egyptian and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indonesian | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, western, fantasy
1. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | musical | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, soul, house
1. the fan of soul is between the fan of reggae and the fan of house##2
2. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | house | soul | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | hedgehog | rat | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, soy-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | 7up | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
